28061FA5.Line7.8354D: They were good. Kind. No different from me or dad.

5A28B31F.Line1.8354D: A torc of protection. I make these for folk who travel the hills alone. Keep them safe with the old blessings.

8E11A623.Line5.8354D: Airidah said all death has meaning. But… where is the meaning in this?

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “A dying man spoke your name and gave me this torc before passing.”

FD1B0C50.VoiceDir5.8354D: Focused, earnest confusion. (Child grappling with meaning of death)
